De_Control Made by SwatMat
This is my best map and my second release. I tried to make this map realistic with realistic lighting and brushwork. --- Thanks to chizbone for the .nav file! --- This is final release, so if you download this map, please tell me if you find any errors or bugs. I also like to know, if this map gets on any server, because I want to see the gameplay, so I can balance it in V2. It's also nice to hear suggestions and features for the V2. --- Screenshot descriptions: 1. T Spawn 2. CT Spawn 3. A Bombsite 4. B Bombsite 5. Tunnel leading B 6. B Bombsite on far right, and A on left.
